It was gathered that the incident happened on Wednesday, July 20, around 10pm when the deceased was on his way back from work. “This happened at Uteh community, off Lucky
The vigilante has been arrested and is currently at the state CID office in Benin.
The entire family is heartbroken and we urge the Edo State Government to ensure this matter isn’t swept under the carpet,” a family source said.
